prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and humorous fantasy beach scene, flat 2D vector illustration style. The setting is a dreamy, ethereal beach at twilight with a pastel pink and soft lavender sky. The ocean is a shimmering turquoise, with gentle, glowing waves. In the center of the scene, a giant, oversized boba milk tea cup sits half-buried in the sand, functioning as a magical hot tub. Inside the boba cup 'hot tub', a charming cartoon-style couple is relaxing. The scene is full of playful, surreal details: the 'bubbles' in the boba cup are iridescent pearls that float gently around the couple, and a tiny, magical waterfall of milk tea cascades from a floating seashell into the cup. Palm trees on the beach have glowing fairy lights strung between them, and instead of coconuts, they grow tiny, colorful boba tea cups. The sand is scattered with sparkling starfish and glowing seashells. In the sky, a friendly cartoon whale floats by, carrying a birthday banner in its mouth. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao". The overall vibe is magical, lighthearted, and funny, with a soft, dreamy color palette.
